data.description: $5000 towards buyers closing! Plus a $3900 Rate buy down available with preferred Lender!  Wonderful Home with Amazing Yard. All New Kitchen... new cabinets, new Granite, new sink, new backsplash.  All new flooring on the main level.  Open floor plan with Formal dining room, breakfast room, and main level office.  Huge level backyard and large deck.  3 car garage!  Generous bedrooms and great bonus room with built-ins.  Walnut Grove is an active community with sidewalks, Club house and Community Pool.  Great Schools.  Come and Look!
